arStrings.szText:
You accumulate {c_number}[{SF_0} * 100/{SF_1}|%|]{/c} of your Maximum Life {c_number}([Max(1,PlayerHealthMax() * SF_0/SF_1)]){/c} as {c_important}{u}Barrier{/u}{/c} every second, up to {c_number}[{SF_0} * 100|%|]{/c} {c_number}([Max(1,PlayerHealthMax() * SF_0)]){/c}.

Taking damage prevents additional accumulation for {c_number}[{SF_2}]{/c} seconds.
